node.text:
Hey StarReaders! 😉 ⭐ 
We hope you didn't miss our first & second episode from the Star Stable Master Class with author @helenadahlgrenofficial. Here's the first episode for you to learn from now or save for later, to enjoy during your cozy weekend! 📖

If you've already dived into our Star Stable Master Class, we're happy to let you know that Episodes 3 & 4 will come out soon, stay tuned! 🤩

Not only is this Star Stable Master Class full of awesome advice, but we hope it encourages you to write your own story! Put your learnings to the test by joining our ongoing storytelling challenge. Take part in our short
story competition for the chance to have your story turned into an
Instagram comic by illustrator Elli Puukangaas! @ellipuukangas #SSOStoryTellers #ReadWriteUnite

node.title: Star Stable Master Class: From reader to writer

node.text:
Star Stable is turning 10 and you're invited to our birthday celebrations kicking off this Wednesday! 🥳  We’ve been making memories together in Jorvik since Star Stable Online launched in 2011. 

Without you, we wouldn’t be here. So we’re marking this incredible milestone by celebrating you. And because it’s a big moment, we’re celebrating big! 🤩 We’ve got loads of fun stuff and surprises in store for you. Enjoy events, gifts, offers, and surprises over four weeks of festivities. Check back here regularly to make sure you don’t miss a thing. We’re hardly able to contain our excitement, so let’s start the countdown! 🎂

Next up in Jorvik! 📣 We have some amazing content coming up for our birthday celebrations! Take a sneak peek at the exciting things on their way to Jorvik! 👀
#NextUpInJorvik

10th birthday!
Happy birthday to Star Stable Online! We’re celebrating 10 enchanting years with an epic party, a FREE horse, birthday items, freebies, and more!

Steve's Farm Revamp
Steve has been doing some redecorating and he’s almost ready to show off his hard work. And what better time for a grand reveal than the second week of our birthday celebrations?

New Coat Variations
Our third week of celebration brings SIX new coat variations! These coat colors have been highly requested so we’re bringing them to you all at once.

The Party is Still On
The horses arrive just in time to attend the party! DJ Kai will be on the dancefloor 24/7. Tired of dancing? Try sending ethereal lanterns into the sky or taking pictures at the photo booth!

Treasure Hunt and Chit Chat
There’s even more for week four! Are you any good at solving riddles? A treasure hunt awaits you and your friends. Mingle with the party guests for some chit-chat. Learn more about them and discover Jorvik lore!

(Featuring the brand-new song, "Celebration" by Dj Kai featuring Nomi, Lisa Peterson, and The Miscreants! @starstablerecords)

If you’ve used this code before, you can’t use it again, and it only applies if you’re not a Star Rider right now. But rest assured, more amazing anniversary offers are headed your way the next few weeks!

node.text:
Hey StarFam! The all-new American Paint has arrived!
There’s nothing quite like a horse and rider roaming freely together, with nothing else before them but inviting grassy plains and the backdrop of a snow-capped mountain range. For the American Paint Horse, this is where they’re in their element. The American Paint horse shares a close ancestry with other popular North American breeds like the American Quarter Horse and American Thoroughbred and therefore shares their long history of aiding humans in shaping North America into the land it is today. They’re strong and easygoing as well as intelligent, making them a fun and rewarding breed to train. Are you ready to bond with this reliable roamer of the American plains? #ColorMePaint

★ Where can I get it?
The Riding Hall! This is a temporary location for now. We’ll find them a permanent place in a later update.
★ How much does it cost?
850 Star Coins.
★ What colors can I choose from?
Dark Bay Tobiano, Chestnut Overo, Black Tobiano, Buckskin Tobiano, Grullo Tobiano, and Dapple Grey Tobiano.

We have new tack to pair with your Paint! With its renowned history in North America and western events, these recolors of Western tack suit the Paint perfectly. There are four matching sets with new halters, blankets, boots, and saddles! Find them at the Global Store and tack store at Starshine Ranch.

Keep on reading at starstable.com to find out more about this week’s update!

If you need inspiration for what to post for a couple of weeks, this might help! Our wonderful @gamingbyesme has created a bunch of prompts on her page for you to jump in and create, and this one is all about horses! 😍

Join every day or just pick the numbers you like the best and post ANYTHING related to the subject, you can’t go wrong; it’s all about how you interpret the topic!
